      "Residents have complained that the same stretches are repaired repeatedly every year without a permanent solution.",
      "Shopkeepers in affected areas reported that poor road conditions have reduced customer footfall and increased vehicle damage.",
      "Urban planning experts suggested that road repair, drain desilting, and utility work should be coordinated before the monsoon season.",
      "The civic body has asked residents to report damaged stretches through the official complaint helpline and mobile application.",
      "Officials stated that complaints related to waterlogging and damaged roads will be reviewed daily until the situation improves."
